OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe night
OL,6,Fwill stay mostly cloudy, with some
OL,7,Foccasional patchy rain during the
OL,8,Fevening which will become more
OL,9,Fwidespread and heavy at times after
OL,10,Fmidnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with locally heavy rain
OL,13,Fat times during the morning. The
OL,14,Fafternoon will become brighter as the
OL,15,Frain clears north, a few showers still
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
